title: Jackson homer leads Cubs to 5-3 win over Reds (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 53,993 Jackson homer leads Cubs to 5-3 win over Reds (Yahoo Sports) CINCINNATI (AP) -- Austin Jackson hit a three-run homer, Anthony Rizzo added an RBI double and the Chicago Cubs kept alive their slim hopes for home-field advantage in the wild-card game with a 5-3 victory over the Cincinnati Reds on Thursday.
